<apex:page docType="html-5.0" 
	standardStylesheets="false" 
	applyBodyTag="false" 
	applyHtmlTag="false" 
	showHeader="false" 
	sidebar="false"
	controller="DfsApplicationController">
<html lang="en" ng-app="dfs">
<head>
	<title>Dell Financial Services</title>

	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=11,chrome=1" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no" />

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angular_material/1.0.7/angular-material.min.css"></link>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons"></link>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="{!URLFOR($Resource.DellFinancialServices, '/styles/app.min.css')}"></link>
</head>
<body ng-cloak="true" layout="column" ng-controller="AppController as app">
    <div flex="true" layout="row">
        <md-sidenav id="dfs-left-sidebar" 
        	md-component-id="left-sidebar" 
        	md-is-locked-open="app.isMedia('gt-xs')" 
        	ng-class="{'dfs-sidebar-sm': app.isMedia('sm') && app.isSidenavClosed('left-sidebar')}"
        	class="md-hue-2 md-whiteframe-z2">
			<md-toolbar>
				<div class="md-toolbar-tools dfs-sidebar-header">
					<h1 layout="row">
						<span class="dfs-icon-dell"></span>
						Financial Services
					</h1>
				</div>
			</md-toolbar>
			<div layout-padding="true" class="dfs-sidebar-userinfo">
				<div layout="column">
					<h2 class="md-title dfs-userinitials sidebar-sm">PH</h2>
					<h2 class="md-title sidebar-gt-sm">Patrick Hanks</h2>
					<span class="md-caption sidebar-gt-sm">patrick_hanks@dell.com</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="dfs-sidebar-nav">
				<md-list flex="true" role="list">
					<md-list-item class="md-1-line" md-ink-ripple="true" ng-click="null">
						<i class="material-icons">account_circle</i>
						<span class="sidebar-gt-sm">
							My Profile
						</span>
					</md-list-item>
					<md-list-item class="md-1-line" md-highlight="true" md-ink-ripple="true" ng-click="null">
						<i class="material-icons">style</i>
						<span class="sidebar-gt-sm">
							Accounts
						</span>
					</md-list-item>
					<md-list-item class="md-1-line" md-ink-ripple="true" ng-click="null">
						<i class="material-icons">lock</i>
						<span class="sidebar-gt-sm">
							Security
						</span>
					</md-list-item>
					<md-list-item class="md-1-line" md-ink-ripple="true" ng-click="null">
						<i class="material-icons">restore</i>
						<span class="sidebar-gt-sm">
							Alerts
						</span>
					</md-list-item>
					<md-list-item class="md-1-line" md-ink-ripple="true" ng-click="null">
						<i class="material-icons">settings</i>
						<span class="sidebar-gt-sm">
							Settings
						</span>
					</md-list-item>
					<md-list-item id="signout" class="md-1-line" md-ink-ripple="true" ng-href="{!$Site.Prefix}/secur/logout.jsp">
						<i class="material-icons">exit_to_app</i>
						<span class="sidebar-gt-sm">
							Sign Out
						</span>
					</md-list-item>
				</md-list>
			</div>
        </md-sidenav>

        <md-content flex="true" layout="column" id="dfs-container">
			<md-toolbar id="dfs-toolbar" class="md-hue-1 md-whiteframe-1dp">
				<div class="md-toolbar-tools md-toolbar-tools-bottom">
					<md-button id="menu-toggle" 
						class="md-icon-button md-primary" 
						hide-gt-sm="true" 
						ng-click="app.toggleSidenav('left-sidebar')">
						<i class="material-icons">menu</i>
					</md-button>
					<h3>Accounts</h3>
				</div>
			</md-toolbar>
			<md-content id="dfs-content" flex="true" layout-padding="true" class="md-hue-1">
				{!$User.Username}
				<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Cras aliquet placerat augue ut porttitor. Suspendisse pellentesque scelerisque odio, non euismod mi consequat et. Integer magna orci, semper a tincidunt fermentum, varius sed libero. In et ultrices leo. Cras rhoncus, mauris ut posuere vehicula, libero mauris commodo augue, et ullamcorper lorem erat quis elit. Interdum et malesuada fames ac ante ipsum primis in faucibus. Maecenas volutpat libero sit amet dignissim porttitor. Praesent quis nulla sollicitudin, vestibulum felis ac, consequat nisi. Sed sit amet auctor eros. Proin dapibus quam lorem, at congue nisl ultricies id. Maecenas id dui interdum, cursus eros at, pretium ligula. Curabitur at purus eros. Morbi lacinia elit et tortor convallis imperdiet. Nam aliquam pretium diam eget gravida.</p>
			</md-content>
        </md-content>
    </div>

    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.5.3/angular.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.5.3/angular-aria.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.5.3/angular-animate.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angular_material/1.0.7/angular-material.min.js"></script>

	<script src="{!URLFOR($Resource.DellFinancialServices, '/app.min.js')}"></script>
	
	<script type="text/javascript">
		(function (angular) {
			angular.module('dfs')
				.constant('dfsConfig', {
					sitePrefix: '{!$Site.prefix}' || '/apex',
					resource: "{!URLFOR($Resource.DellFinancialServices)}"
				});
		})(angular);
	</script>
</body>
</html>
</apex:page>